snippet.title: Twenty One Pilots - Overcompensate (Official Video)
snippet.description:
"Overcompensate" the first single from the forthcoming album, Clancy, available everywhere May 17. 

Pre-Order Clancy: https://TOP.lnk.to/Clancy
Stream/Download "Overcompensate": https://TOP.lnk.to/Clancy

LYRICS
Earned my stripes, 300 tracks in my Adidas track jacket,
Bless your ear holes while you react,
Acting gobsmacked don’t hesitate to maybe overcompensate,
I feel like I was just here, same twitching in my eyes,
Don’t sleep on a boy who can’t fall asleep twice,
In the same night and won’t hesitate to maybe overcompensate.

I fly by the dangerous bend symbol,
Don’t hesitate to maybe overcompensate,
And then by the time I catch in my peripheral,
Don’t hesitate to maybe overcompensate.

Where am I from? I was born right here, just now,
Originated right in front of your eyes,
If you can’t see, I am Clancy,
Prodigal son, done running, come up with Josh Dun,
Wanted dead or alive,
So now you pick who you serve,
You bow to the masses,
Get kicked to the curb,
For passing the classes,
Half empty, half full, save half for your taxes,
Then overtake your former self.

Days feel like a perfect length,
I don’t need them any longer,
but for goodness sake,
Do the years seem
way too short for my soul,
corazón.

snippet.title: アニメ『ワンパンマン』第3期特報 / One-Punch Man Season 3 Special Announcement
snippet.description:
最強VS最恐
アニメ『ワンパンマン』第3期　制作進行中
■STORY
趣味でヒーローを始めた男、サイタマ。3年間の特訓により、あらゆる敵を一撃（ワンパン）で倒す無敵のパワーを手に入れた彼は、ひょんなことから弟子となったジェノスと共に、職業としてのヒーローが所属する組織・ヒーロー協会に入り、日々活動している。
そんなある日、突如現れた怪人協会を名乗る怪人達に幹部の子供を人質に取られてしまったヒーロー協会。S級ヒーロー達が集まり、人質奪還のために怪人協会のアジトへの突入作戦が練られる。一方、ヒーロー達との戦いの最中怪人協会に連れ去られた“人間怪人”ガロウは、そのアジトで目を覚ます。
■STAFF
原作：ONE・村田雄介「ワンパンマン」（集英社「となりのヤングジャンプ」連載）
シリーズ構成：鈴木智尋／キャラクターデザイン：久保田誓、黒田新次郎、白川亮介／音楽：宮崎誠
アニメーション制作：J.C.STAFF
■CAST
サイタマ：古川慎／ガロウ：緑川光／ジーナス博士：浪川大輔
----
■STORY
Saitama is a hero who only became a hero for fun.
After three years of "special training," hes become so strong that he's practically invincible. In fact, he's too strong—even his mightiest opponents are taken out with a single punch. Alongside Genos, his faithful disciple, Saitama performs his official hero duties as a member of the Hero Association.
One day, monsters claiming to be from the Monster Association suddenly appeared, taking a child of  Hero Association executive as a hostage. The S-class heroes gather and plan a raid on the Monster Association hideout to rescue the hostage. Meanwhile, Garou, a "human monster" who was taken by the Monster Association during a battle with the heroes, awakens in the Monster Association hideout.
■STAFF
Based on "One-Punch Man" by ONE and Yusuke Murata (serialized in "Tonarino Young Jump" published by SHUEISHA)
Series Composition: Tomohiro Suzuki
Character Design: Chikashi Kubota, Shinjiro Kuroda, Ryosuke Shirakawa
Music: Makoto Miyazaki
Animation Studio: J.C.STAFF
■CAST
Saitama: Makoto Furukawa / Garou: Hikaru Midorikawa
Doctor Genus (Narration): Daisuke Namikawa
＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿＿
◆Official Website: http://onepunchman-anime.net
◆Official Twitter: @opm_anime
◆Official Instagram: opm_anime
© ONE, Yusuke Murata/SHUEISHA, Hero Association HQ

snippet.title: LAKERS at CLIPPERS | FULL GAME HIGHLIGHTS | February 28, 2024
snippet.description:
Despite trailing 98-77 at the 11:45 mark in the 4th quarter, the Lakers rallied behind LeBron James who outscored the Clippers by himself, 19-16, while the Lakers totaled 39 points overall in the 4th quarter and won, 116-112. LeBron James totaled 34 points (season-high 7 3PT;  19 PTS and 5 3PT in Q4 alone), 6 rebounds, and 8 assists as Anthony Davis added 20 points, 12 rebounds, and 3 blocks. Kawhi Leonard led the Clippers with 26 points, 7 rebounds, and 6 assists while James Harden added 23 points and 9 assists. The Lakers improve to 32-28 as the Clippers move to 37-20.

Gaami Trailer On UV Creations.

#Gaami chronicles the adventurous journey of Shankar- a wounded, reluctant and reclusive Aghora on his quest to find the cure for his very rare condition- ‘an inability to experience any human touch’.  But this adventure for cure would be fulfilled, only when he can confront and conquer his destiny that becomes intertwined with two other characters.

snippet.title: I Gained Weight, So I Committed To 30 Days Of Healthy Habits
snippet.description:
Over the holidays I gained weight. I decided to commit to 30 days of healthy habits to get back on track. 

Protein PB&J Roll Ups 
- 40g Kodiak pancake mix 
- 1 scoop protein powder
- 50g egg whites 
- 50g cashew milk 
- sprinkle of cinnamon 

*mix until all ingredients are combined. 
* pour mixture in to a pan with some oil/ spray on medium high heat.Then move the mixture around to cover the bottom of the entire pan. 
* let cook on each side for around 3-4 minutes 
* Spread peanut butter and jam on top then roll up. 


Cajun Chicken Orzo 
- 1/2 cup red onion 
- 1/2 cup green pepper 
- 1 heap tbs cajun seasoning 
- 1/4 cup sun dried tomato 
- 1 heap tbs tomato paste 
- 1/2 cup orzo 
- 1 cup hot chicken broth 

* Sautee red onion and green pepper in a pot until a little soft then add your cajun seasoning a mix well 
* Add chicken, sundried tomato, tomato paste and orzo to the pot and mix until everything looks evenly coated 
* Pour in hot chicken broth, mix together and then cover and let simmer and cook for around 15 minutes or more 
* Once cooked add in a slurry of 2tbs cashew milk & 1 tbs corn starch that's well combined into your pot. this will give it a thick creamy texture.
